{"tid":2486561,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【蝕讓成交】5年蝕183萬！西貢半新樓逸瓏園套3房1238萬成交","createTime":"2021-04-13T03:24:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T11:41:13.000Z","uid":24730,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2e3af0a0a36558eb780d5c3a2f6f7b9ae3cbcfab","tid":2486561,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:24:17.000Z","msg":"【蝕讓成交】5年蝕183萬！西貢半新樓逸瓏園套3房1238萬成交<br />\n<br />\n私樓成交<br />\n08:07 2021/04/13<br />\n讚好1<br />\n疫情走勢緩和，但西貢區新晉屋苑卻出現蝕讓成交。世紀21奇豐物業西貢區營業董事廖振雄表示，西貢逸瓏園屬區內低密度豪宅，新近錄得1座中層J室成交，實用面積1,003平方呎，3房套房2廳連儲物室間隔，望園景。原開價1,330萬元，累減92萬元，減幅6.9%，最終以1,238萬元沽出，實用面積呎價12,343元。原業主於2016年5月購入上址，當時作價1,421萬元，持貨5年至今轉售帳面蝕183萬元。<br />\n<br />\n責任編輯：陳嘉敏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2929808/%E3%80%90%E8%9D%95%E8%AE%93%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E3%80%915%E5%B9%B4%E8%9D%95183%E8%90%AC%EF%BC%81%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E5%8D%8A%E6%96%B0%E6%A8%93%E9%80%B8%E7%93%8F%E5%9C%92%E5%A5%973%E6%88%BF1238%E8%90%AC%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2929808%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E3%2580%25915%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%259D%2595183%25E8%2590%25AC%25EF%25BC%2581%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25B2%25A2%25E5%258D%258A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25A8%2593%25E9%2580%25B8%25E7%2593%258F%25E5%259C%2592%25E5%25A5%25973%25E6%2588%25BF1238%25E8%2590%25AC%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DGo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=e9635179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2929808/%E3%80%90%E8%9D%95%E8%AE%93%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E3%80%915%E5%B9%B4%E8%9D%95183%E8%90%AC%EF%BC%81%E8%A5%BF%E8%B2%A2%E5%8D%8A%E6%96%B0%E6%A8%93%E9%80%B8%E7%93%8F%E5%9C%92%E5%A5%973%E6%88%BF1238%E8%90%AC%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4</a>"},{"pid":"492995868bb8844e9075132fbc262c77f9cd1957","tid":2486561,"uid":345941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T03:27:39.000Z","msg":"可唔可以攞啲正常樓去比較？<img src=\"/assets/faces/p